<item>
            <title>[LU-1627] Change lbuild to use https://github.com/zfsonlinux to fetch spl/zfs source</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1627</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lbuild fetches zfs/spl source using git@github.com:zfsonlinux which requires a ssh keypair with git hub. If we change this to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/zfsonlinux&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/zfsonlinux&lt;/a&gt; then we will not need local keys for github as part of the builds.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The option to change the default by using SPLZFSGITREPO should be kept.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So change&lt;br/&gt;
git clone ${SPLZFSGITREPO:-&quot;git@github.com:zfsonlinux&quot;}/$pkg.git $pkg 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1&lt;br/&gt;
to&lt;br/&gt;
git clone ${SPLZFSGITREPO:-&quot;https://github.com/zfsonlinux&quot;}/$pkg.git $pkg 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
